
& piloting-aerospace
 
 >> Help: Piloting-Aerospace (Piloting Skill)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Used for piloting rolls while in a VTOL (such as landing, etc.).
 
 To see specifics on vtol units, type 'help vtol'.
 
 For a detailed look at this skill, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
